## ğŸ”§ KonfigÃ¼rasyon

### config.yaml
```yaml
model:
  name: "cardiffnlp/twitter-xlm-roberta-base-sentiment"
  cache_dir: "./models"
  
preprocessing:
  lowercase: true
  remove_urls: true
  remove_mentions: true
  
output:
  confidence_threshold: 0.6
  export_format: "csv"
```

